column5: Pretty cool footage from In-Fisherman.  Don't think that smallie is gonna make it.  Muskie Eats Smallmouth
Wow...that smallie got rocked!  I think I'd be letting buddy net that fish...as opposed to putting my hand under it
cool they got the musky on film...  this happens in certain areas on the larry... happened to me 2 weeks ago...
This has happened to be more then a few times on the French River when bringing in smallies.  I've had a few devoured by 50+ inch monsters.
Great footage, does seem to happen frequently on St Clair
Image the video if he had an underwater camera for that ! hope the bass recovered
Cool vid!  I've had them hit my trolling motor, more then once.
Thats' pretty cool, thanks for posting it.
Awesome!! On my last outting, i had 2   36+ Pike slide in from 2 different directions,wanting the perch on the end of my line. Its a creepy feeling i'll tell ya
there is no way id be reaching in to grab that bass...lol.. I love the"oh no, what are we gonna do here"...Thanks for sharing by the way!
I definitely wouldn't go skinny dipping there!!!
Ya. my hand would have stayed well out of the water in that situation...  Cool video!
That is very cool Had it happen once when fishing out of a Canoe & its like what do you do next lol  SBK
